  "detailed_description": "<h1>Reviews</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>8/10</strong></h2> GameReactor<br>\"The game doesn't take itself too seriously at all, and it's a good laugh... Shooty Fruity is executed well!\"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>9/10</strong></h2> GamingNexus<br>\"As many shooters as there are in the VR space, very few are as flat out frantic and entertaining as this.\"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>8.5/10</strong></h2> PCAficionado<br>\"Shooty Fruity – High quality VR gaming at its best.\"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>8/10</strong></h2> CriticalHitGaming<br>\"It’s tense, exciting, and silly – and some of the most fun I’ve had with VR this year.\"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>8/10</strong></h2> Hardcore Gamer<br>\"Expertly blends together classic shooting galleries with much-appreciated bits of strategy\"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>9/10</strong></h2> Codec Moments<br>\"It's loud, frantic and brilliant... you'll find nothing else like it!\"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4.5/5</strong></h2> The VR Base<br>\"Shooty Fruity is Savagely Fun\"</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/1_TAGLINE_ENG.PNG?t=1667464400\" /></span><br>Scan, serve & pack produce whilst shooting guns to defend your store from mutant fruit!<br><br>Shooty Fruity is a multi-tasking shooter only possible with a VR headset & motion control. Can you do your job as a sharpshooting shop clerk during the heat of combat? Take on new roles, unlock new weapons & blow up tons of fruit in your juicy career. Scan! Shoot! Repeat!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/9a932ac09a6f9b60ad7b1dc504929d01.poster.avif?t=1667464400\" width=600 height=357 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/9a932ac09a6f9b60ad7b1dc504929d01.webm?t=1667464400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/2_TEXT_HEADER_A_ENG.PNG?t=1667464400\" /></span><br>New “shoot & serve” multi-tasking gameplay made especially for VR & motion control. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/3_SCREENSHOTS_A_B_ENG.PNG?t=1667464400\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/4_TEXT_HEADER_B_ENG.PNG?t=1667464400\" /></span><br>Work through a whole career of roles & challenges, including checkout, canteen & more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/5_SCREENSHOTS_C_ENG.PNG?t=1667464400\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/6_TEXT_HEADER_C_ENG.PNG?t=1667464400\" /></span><br>Arm yourself with a customisable arsenal of fruit-killing guns, explosives & power-ups. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/ef469c3033cfd9fd828e7fdb2ae120e3.avif?t=1667464400\" width=599 height=334 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/8_TEXT_HEADER_D_ENG.PNG?t=1667464400\" /></span><br>Tons of vicious, nasty fruit! Unload high octane ammo into their ripe, fleshy bodies!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/666100/extras/9_SCREENSHOTS_F_ENG.PNG?t=1667464400\" /></span><br><br>Interested in more VR games and experiences?  Check out the rest of the nDreams VR catalogue here!<br><br> Available for Arcades on SpringboardVR ",
